{"tid":1050339,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇格蘭銀行及大學收可疑包裹　需緊急疏散","createTime":"2019-03-07T00:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T00:26:19.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"25fe673fa8377cb8720352287e27ba82bb5b6b36","tid":1050339,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T00:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190306/photo/bkn-20190306210309833-0306_00912_001_01b.jpg?20190306214402\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190306%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190306210309833-0306_00912_001_01b.jpg%3F20190306214402&h=c3b72924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方封鎖現場。（互聯網）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190306/photo/bkn-20190306210309833-0306_00912_001_02b.jpg?20190306214402\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190306%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190306210309833-0306_00912_001_02b.jpg%3F20190306214402&h=9ba9800c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多輛警車在場戒備。（互聯網）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190306/photo/bkn-20190306210309833-0306_00912_001_03b.jpg?20190306214402\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190306%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190306210309833-0306_00912_001_03b.jpg%3F20190306214402&h=1a8ce52b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學生慌忙逃生。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n繼英國倫敦3個交通樞紐周二（5日）發現爆炸品後，蘇格蘭格拉斯哥大學及蘇格蘭皇家銀行總部分別於周三（6日）收到可疑包裹，需緊急疏散。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，校方在郵件收發室發現可疑包裹，學生於當地時間早上11時左右，收到疏散指示要求他們離開校園，有人穿着白袍趕忙逃走。目擊者憶述，警方接報到場後封鎖附近道路，並大叫讓學生及教職員盡快逃離學校大樓，附近停泊了多輛應變車輛。<br />\n<br />\n蘇格蘭皇家銀行總部亦差不多於同一時間、即早上約11時收到可疑包裹，職員需要緊急疏散，但其後發現是誤報。現時兩個包裹正由爆炸品專家檢驗，相信大學及銀行的案件沒有關連，目前未知案件與倫敦一案是否有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190306/bkn-20190306210309833-0306_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190306%2Fbkn-20190306210309833-0306_00912_001.html&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QLidffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=a31a065f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190306/bkn-20190306210309833-0306_00912_001.html</a>"}]}